OL,3,C'Questions left unanswered' at South
OL,4,CWest Water meeting, residents say
OL,6,FResidents in Brixham who attended a
OL,7,Fmeeting with South West Water (SWW) to
OL,8,Fdiscuss the water parasite outbreak in
OL,9,Fsouth Devon said it's left too many
OL,10,Fquestions unanswered.
OL,12,FSWW bosses - including Chief Executive
OL,13,FSusan Davy - faced a series of
OL,14,Fquestions about the outbreak of
OL,15,Fcryptosporidium during a meeting at
OL,16,FBrixham Town Hall on Thursday 12
OL,17,FSeptember.
