OL,3,C'Questions left unanswered' at South
OL,4,CWest Water meeting, residents say
OL,6,FIt has been nine weeks since the last
OL,7,Fhouseholds in Brixham were told their
OL,8,Ftap water was safe to drink following
OL,9,Fthe discovery of the parasite in May.
OL,11,FCaroline Voaden, the Liberal Democrat
OL,12,FMP for South Devon, said residents
OL,13,Fhave had to wait too long to put their
OL,14,Fquestions to Ms Davy, but hopes there
OL,15,Fwill be progress in the coming months.
OL,17,FSWW said it was "truly sorry" for the
OL,18,Fsignificant impact the outbreak had on
OL,19,Flocal people and business.
