OL,3,C'Questions left unanswered' at South
OL,4,CWest Water meeting, residents say
OL,6,FShe said: "The main question, that
OL,7,Fcame right at the end, was a lot of
OL,8,Fpeople asking whether their water was
OL,9,Fsafe. We've got no trust in the water
OL,10,Fthat we're drinking."
OL,12,FMs Voaden said she believed Brixham is
OL,13,Fstill struggling to trust SWW.
OL,15,FShe said: "If they find that the cause
OL,16,Fof this outbreak was because SWW had
OL,17,Fnot maintained the equipment, then I
OL,18,Fabsolutely think Ms Davy should go
OL,19,Fbecause I think she has to take
OL,20,Fresponsibility for that.
