OL,3,C'Questions left unanswered' at South
OL,4,CWest Water meeting, residents say
OL,6,F"I think there is a question around
OL,7,Fcorporate governance. What is a water
OL,8,Fcompany for?"
OL,10,FIn a statement, David Harris, Managing
OL,11,FDirector of Water Services, said: "We
OL,12,Fknow the rare events in Brixham
OL,13,Fearlier this year had a significant
OL,14,Fimpact on local people and businesses
OL,15,Fand for that we are truly sorry.
