OL,3,C'Questions left unanswered' at South
OL,4,CWest Water meeting, residents say
OL,6,F"While the situation has thankfully
OL,7,Fbeen resolved, we know some people may
OL,8,Fstill have questions. We organised
OL,9,Fthis event to give customers the
OL,10,Fchance to hear from us in person," he
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FThousands of people were left having
OL,14,Fto boil or use bottled water after the
OL,15,Fparasite, which causes sickness and
OL,16,Fdiarrhoea, was first detected.
OL,18,FThe advice remained in place for 54
OL,19,Fdays for some properties before it was
OL,20,Ffinally lifted on 8 July.
